time that students can spend in other activities.</p>'),(170,2022,'en','Installment and Secure Host','Installment payment is a popular method of paying for goods and services that allows customers to spread out the cost of a purchase over a period of time.','<p>Installment payment is a popular method of paying for goods and services that allows customers to spread out the cost of a purchase over a period of time. With installment payment, customers are able to pay for a product or service in smaller, more manageable amounts rather than having to pay the full amount upfront.</p><p><br></p><p>Installment payments are typically made on a monthly basis, and the amount of each payment is determined by the total cost of the purchase and the length of the repayment period. For example, if a customer purchases a product for $1,000 with a repayment period of 12 months, they would make 12 monthly payments of $83.33.</p><p><br></p><p>One of the benefits of installment payment is that it allows customers to make larger purchases that they may not be able to afford upfront. This can be particularly helpful for big-ticket items such as furniture, appliances, or electronics. By spreading out the cost of the purchase, customers can avoid having to pay a large sum of money all at once.</p><p><br></p><p>Another advantage of installment payment is that it can be a good option for customers who want to build their credit history. By making regular, on-time payments, customers can demonstrate their creditworthiness and potentially improve their credit score over time.</p><p><br></p><p>However, it\'s important to note that installment payment may not always be the most cost-effective option. Some installment plans may come with additional fees or higher interest rates than other payment methods. Customers should always read the terms and conditions carefully before agreeing to an installment payment plan to ensure they fully understand the costs involved.</p><p><br></p><p>Overall, installment payment is a flexible and convenient option that can make it easier for customers to make purchases they may not be able to afford upfront. Whether it\'s for a large purchase or to build credit, installment payment is a useful tool for many consumers.</p>'),(171,2023,'en','How to Cook Jollof Rice',NULL,'<p>This is a Jollof Rice Course<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-family-base); font-size: 1rem;\">This is a Jollof Rice Course</span></p>'),(172,2024,'en','Product and Services Design forSME\'s',NULL,'<p>Nice Product</p>'),(173,2025,'en','How to make Bread','Learn the art of bread-making in this comprehensive course. From mixing ingredients to mastering baking techniques, we guide you through each step to create delicious homemade bread.','<p>In this hands-on course, <em>How to Make Bread</em>, youll discover the joy of baking bread from scratch. Designed for beginners and intermediate bakers alike, this course covers everything you need to know to create soft, flavorful loaves at home. We\'ll guide you through essential techniques such as dough preparation, kneading, proofing, and baking, ensuring each step is easy to follow.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify; \">By the end of this course, youll be able to bake a variety of breads with confidence, understand the science behind the ingredients, and have a repertoire of delicious recipes to share with family and friends. Perfect for anyone looking to master homemade bread-making!</p>'),(175,2027,'en','Business Registration and Regulatory Matters','Business Registration and Regulation','<p>This course provides guidance on business registration, focusing on selecting the right form, ensuring regulatory compliance, exploring business structures, and understanding legal frameworks for long-term success.</p>'),(176,2028,'en','Digital Transformation for SMEs: Tools and Tactics for Success','Empower your SME with digital tools and strategies. Learn how to drive growth, boost efficiency, and stay competitive in todays digital world.','<p>In todays fast-paced digital era, small and medium enterprises (SMEs) must embrace digital transformation to stay competitive and thrive. This course is designed to guide SME owners and managers through the essential tools, strategies, and tactics needed to digitally transform their businesses effectively.</p><p>Participants will explore core concepts, including adopting digital tools for productivity, leveraging data to make informed decisions, enhancing customer engagement through digital channels, and implementing cybersecurity measures. Through real-world case studies and practical exercises, youll gain actionable insights on choosing the right digital platforms, managing change within your organization, and creating a culture of innovation.</p><p>Whether you\'re just starting your digital journey or looking to optimize current strategies, this course will equip you with the knowledge and skills to drive sustainable growth and long-term success.</p>');
